[au:]大陆和海洋的真正分界线\n
[02:43.51]occurs at the foot of a steeper slope.\n
[au:]是在陡坡脚下.\n
[02:46.59]This continental slope usually starts at a place somewhere near the 100-fathom mark\n
[au:]大陆架慢坡开始的地方一般是从差不多100英寻水深处,\n
[02:54.16]and in the course of a few hundred miles\n
[au:]一直延伸到几百英里远,\n
